Description: Implements the binomial and Fisher's (2x2 and 2x3 so far) exact
    tests, along with corresponding discrete distributions
    (binomial, hypergeometric).  Accuracy and speed of these functions compare
    favorably to their counterparts in the R 4.6.0 standard library.
